					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>close shave<br /> ˌklōs ˈSHāv/Submit<br /> noun<br /> 1.<br /> a shave in which the hair is cut very short.<br /> 2.<br /> informal<br /> a narrow escape from danger or disaster.</p> </blockquote> <p>Many thanks to my good friend and critter, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=414239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1533422893" alt="Gabriel Jade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=414239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" >Gabriel Jade</a></span>.<br /> Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1533422893" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span> for making sure Tim was in-character and for creating this wonderful group of interest for me to write for.<br /> Shoutout to the r/scpd and Author's Corner discords for being super cool and supportive people.</p> <p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/ringo">Ringo</a> was written by my friend <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hot-coles" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3997195&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1533422893" alt="Hot-coles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3997195)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hot-coles" >Hot-coles</a></span> and <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-1000">SCP-1000</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thedeadlymoose" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=732274&amp;amp;size=small&